channel.description:
I only got one gift, out of two :(. My ipod video 80 Gigs, pff its the same size as my 30 gig that i bought like last year. Thought it broke =(.
Want to see the inside of an ipod! Cracked in half!

So the question is what are YOU getting for christmas, or already gotten, or hoping to get? :P
